title: Contemporary - Adams Point Apt. #15
posting_body: ['Contact info:', 'David Sykes | Meridian Management Group', 'Cell:', 'show contact info', 'BRE #00990193', 'Centrally Located Renovated Adams Point Apt.#15', '301 Jayne Avenue #15', 'Oakland, CA 94610', '$2,725/Month', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Open House Viewings Scheduled by Appointment', '3rd, Top Floor 2BR/2BA', '* Oakland Rent Controlled - Annual lease', '* Shared laundry', '* Shared deck', '* Elevator in building', "* Parking at an add'l fee", "Bright, contemporary, third, top floor 2BR/2BA apartment in Oakland's Adams Point.", 'Floors are hardwood except in bath.', 'Heat is via gas wall heater and floor radiators.', 'Open living room has kitchen in an alcove to one side of the entrance, windows at the opposite end, and one bedroom to each side.', 'Kitchen includes gas stove, dishwasher and microwave.', 'Both bedrooms have wall closets with sliding mirror doors and a private bath with shower-over-tub and sliding glass doors.', 'Building is on a quiet, two-block street just north of Lake Merritt.', 'Each floor has a shared deck overlooking the front of the building.', 'Building has an elevator and parking may be available for an additional fee.', 'The Walk Score is 85.', "Enjoy convenient access to Whole Foods, the Grand Lake Theater, Lake Merritt Farmer's Market on Saturday from 9 am 2 pm, Peet's Coffee, Arizmendi and Trader Joe's (to name a few) for your shopping convenience.", 'Definitely a MUST SEE!', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES', '• Contemporary building', '• Near AC Transit/BART transportation/Hwy 580 Access', '• Nearby carpool to SF', 'LEASE TERMS:', 'Owner pays for water and garbage.', 'Tenants responsible for PGE (electricity and gas) and internet/cable service.', 'Contact info:', 'David Sykes | Meridian Management Group', 'Cell:', 'show contact info', 'BRE #00990193', 'MMG330']
